editor_description = "This watches for object generated by the parent (which should be a `scatterObjectPlacer`. When one is generated, it waits for the new object to be destroyed and then it waits for `respawn_delay_in_milliseconds`  and then causes the parent to regenerate one new child
ie: It respawns deleted things after a delay
For use as child of scatterObjectPlacer.tscn"
